social_posts.post_text: too many special moments to capture in ten frames🇦🇺🥹🫶🏽
A sunrise swim to bring in the new year💫

Last week in Bali I had the pleasure of visiting @chloeorphans 🫶🏽 The 24 children being raised by Pastor Victor and his family are so sweet, intelligent and made me feel welcome in their home.

This orphanage is run completely off donations and I have seen first hand how much they need our help! 

I have provided a link to the donation page on my profile- if you could contribute a small, or not so small donation, it would be put toward their living facility, among other essential needs.

Each time I visit Bali I will make sure I visit my new friends🤍
